# HR Role Sidebar Structure

When working on the HR dashboard/sidebar, keep the menu structure in this exact order and naming:

- Dashboard  
- Calendar  
- Manage Users  
- Employee List  
- PDS Management  
- Leave Applications  
- Learning & Development  
- Reports & Analytics  
- Settings  

The profile section should appear in the sidebar footer as a separate, persistent block (not part of the main menu list).

